original: Zetterström, Tor Helge, arkitekt, Göteborg, f. 17/7/84 i Gbg av C. J. Z. o Maria Andersson. G. m. Ingrid Pettersson. Barn: Rolf Ragnar f. 30. — CTI, Polytechn. Strehtz, Tyskl, 04. Egen verks. s. arkit. o. byggm. i Gbg sed. 12. Medl. av SAR, Tekn. samf. i Gbg o. Byggn:tekn. fören.
translated: Zetterström, Tor Helge, architect, Gothenburg, born on July 17, 1884 in Gothenburg to C.J. Z. and Maria Andersson. Married to Ingrid Pettersson in the year 19xx. Children: Rolf Ragnar, born on the 30th. -CTI, Polytechn. Strehtz, Germany, 1904. Own practice as architect and builder in Gothenburg since 1912. Member of SAR (Swedish Association of Architects), Technical Society in Gothenburg, and Building Technology Association.
